WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:12.510
Just six years old, Kwon Ji-Yeon is recovering
in hospital near the coastal city of Jindo.

00:00:12.510 --> 00:00:17.290
South Korean television has released this
footage of the moment she was rescued from

00:00:17.290 --> 00:00:19.250
the sinking ferry.

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:23.050
She's understood to have been travelling with
her parents and her brother.

00:00:23.050 --> 00:00:26.440
They're still missing.

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:31.550
Kwon Ji-Yeon's image has been widely shared
on social media, with messages calling for

00:00:31.550 --> 00:00:36.120
any of her relatives to come forward.

00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:39.420
An uncle is reported to have made contact
with her.

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:45.019
But there's no news of her immediate family.

